dialogueContent.words: We've been informed there's two main bases for the Biolab. Let's head to the first one and scout it out. And... try not to take any deep breaths out there, Commander.
Good job there, Commander. Let's hope that {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} crew weren't right about that virus.
This virus will be a problem now, Commander. Let's get you back.
There are a few dead bodies scattered around the base here, Commander. I hate to say it but maybe there's something going on with this biolab. Let's check the biolab complex.
*** DETECTED UNKNOWN FORCE *** ... *** VIRUS BREACH DETECTED *** .... *** ACTIVATING DEVICE NETWORK ***
Watch out, Commander! Turrets coming online!
We knew your damned experiments here would ruin us, {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym}. Now you've released that virus and killed us all. At least we'll take you with us first.
*** DETECTED UNKNOWN FORCE *** ... *** VIRUS DETECTED *** .... *** ACTIVATING DEVICE NETWORK ***
What was all that about a virus? To be on the safe side I wouldn't leave your mechs whilst you're down there. Let's move to the biolab complex to figure this out.
A {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} attack? Virus? What the hell is going on here? Let's get this over with fast.
Unidentified BattleMech lance. This base has been put under quarantine by {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName}. Leave this area now.
{TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} radio operator. You have illegally taken over this {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} base. Leave or be forced out.
You leave us no choice. Contain and control those Mercs!
Watch out, Commander! Base defenses are coming online!
*** DETECTED OCCUPYING FORCE *** ... *** VIRUS DETECTED ON OCCUPYING UNITS *** .... *** ACTIVATING DEVICE NETWORK ***
Commander! Are we glad to see you! {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} Biolab {TGT_SYSTEM.name}-Delta.

We had a containment breach on one of our projects. Nothing serious I assure you and we have it under control. However, it looks like we've pushed the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} watchers too far. They're determined to wipe us out!

longDescription: Bio research station? We better be careful here, Commander. I don't fancy catching a new type of cold, if you know what I mean?

shortDescription: One of our bio research stations has gone dark in the {TGT_SYSTEM.name} system. We've not sure why but {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} affiliated groups have been asking about purchasing some specific supplies we also use in that system. Investigate and find out what's going on.
